The synthetic dataset files in this directory are dedicated to the public domain under CC0 1.0 Universal unless explicitly stated otherwise.

This includes generated images, COCO annotations, prediction files, precomputed metrics, saved CV Model Lab project files, and generated sample reports contained in this directory.

No real photographs, private data, or third-party visual assets are intentionally included in these synthetic datasets.

